response.original_title: Rocking the Boat: The Story of Lily Lee Chen
response.overview: Lisa Ling introduces the heroine of politics in the USA. For generations, Monterey Park has been a city of light for immigrants from AA communities. Now a two part series on the first Asian American politician is here on Montageplay.com look for more AAPI leaders like Grace Yoo who is running for City Councilwoman of Los Angeles in Koreatown District. Watching and voting it's an important thing to do!
